Global Disodium 1,5-Naphthalenedisulfonate Market Insights
Disodium 1,5-Naphthalenedisulfonate Market size was valued at USD 1.2 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Disodium 1,5-Naphthalenedisulfonate Market Overview
The global market for Disodium 1,5-Naphthalenedisulfonate is experiencing steady growth, driven by its wide application in industries such as water treatment, dyes, and as an intermediate in chemical synthesis. The market size was valued at approximately USD 300 million in 2023, with projections to reach around USD 400 million by 2028, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.5%. This growth is supported by increasing demand from developing regions for water treatment solutions and the rising use of naphthalene derivatives in industrial processes. Additionally, the market’s expansion is attributed to its ability to enhance the stability and effectiveness of chemical formulations, driving growth across various sectors. The increasing need for eco-friendly and sustainable solutions is further augmenting the market, providing new opportunities for suppliers.

